Welcome to Chevening Parish Council's website. Chevening Parish encompasses Chevening & Chipstead villages, Bessels Green and part of Goathurst Common towards Ide Hill. 

We have no shops but we have 5 pubs and 3 different denominations of Worship, Chevening Church, Bessels Green Baptist Church and Sevenoaks Unitarians
